title: I'll Name This Podcast Later Episode 7
description: After last week's childhood redemption; Joe, Marisa, & Rory discuss the Summer Jam line up, a weekend full of shots (or lack there of), & Jay-Z's new streaming service "TIDAL". Did Joe close with Alma? Spoiler alert: No.
